            "id": 5898364,
            "title": "台積電被逼救INTEL！台股恐崩or狂飆？輝達GTC受惠股引爆新行情！",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"335\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"2.065671641791045\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/m/ff8d6d8e5f15d05d54f87d2d67ecf240.jpg\" data-width=\"692\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/l/ff8d6d8e5f15d05d54f87d2d67ecf240.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普上任後，投資人期待的降稅與金融鬆綁未落實，反而不斷加碼關稅，導致科技股大跌，蘋果、輝達、META、Google、特斯拉股價重挫，其中特斯拉因馬斯克力挺川普，成為全球抵制對象，跌幅逾 50%。美股四大指數探底，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>回測年線，短線有機會技術性反彈。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"353\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.954674220963173\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/m/0ab69b9fdaa68cc4adcb3d131673ce58.jpg\" data-width=\"690\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/l/0ab69b9fdaa68cc4adcb3d131673ce58.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電投資美國 1000 億美元後，仍被迫處理 Intel 晶圓代工問題，與輝達、AMD、博通合組新公司。此舉恐壓縮毛利率、營益率，拖累台股震盪。不過，相較於 100% 關稅衝擊，影響仍在可控範圍內，台積電短線整理，長線依舊看好。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"335\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"2.065671641791045\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/m/3f4c61325c10aef0f5f7646717ba8d30.jpg\" data-width=\"692\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/l/3f4c61325c10aef0f5f7646717ba8d30.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股的部分，外資連十賣，累計賣超逾 3000 億，短線利空消化中，技術面年線出現假跌破，短線反彈機率高，預計於 22,000-23,500 點震盪。台積電盤整，資金轉進中小型股，如 LINE PAY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:7722:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7722\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7722-TW</a>)大漲 118%、辣椒 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4946:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4946\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4946-TW</a>) 上漲 114%，皆具「低位階、量滾量、題材支撐」三特徵。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>下週一 (3/17) 輝達 GTC 大會登場，受惠股有京元電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2449:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2449-TW</a>)、廣達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、奇鋐(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3017-TW</a>)、立端(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6245:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6245\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6245-TW</a>)、聯發科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)、緯穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>) 等。我已整理完整受惠名單，含本益比、殖利率等資訊，免費提供！點擊 LINE 連結，回覆「888」，立即領取！</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>➤鼎極操盤手 何基鼎 LINE 粉絲團</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://lin.ee/iuxMCJU\">https://lin.ee/iuxMCJU</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>➤鼎極操盤手 何基鼎 YT</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@gd1788\">https://www.youtube.com/@gd1788</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"912\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.7587719298245614\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/m/429937a2947906039a64e83ffa0c2d2c.jpg\" data-width=\"692\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/l/429937a2947906039a64e83ffa0c2d2c.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"428\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.7757009345794392\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/m/0a0de3af2a6ead1444e61ac34ce2df2f.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5898364/l/0a0de3af2a6ead1444e61ac34ce2df2f.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"warning\">本公司所推薦分析之個別有價證券 無不當之財務利益關係 以往之績效不保證未來獲利 投資人應獨立判斷 審慎評估並自負投資風險</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
